net.sf.jclec.problem.classification

Interface IClassifierIndividual

  • All Superinterfaces:
    net.sf.jclec.IIndividual, net.sf.jclec.JCLEC, java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ExprTreeRuleIndividual, MultiExprTreeRuleIndividual, MultiSyntaxTreeRuleIndividual, SyntaxTreeRuleIndividual

    public interface IClassifierIndividual
extends net.sf.jclec.IIndividual
    Individual definition for evolutionary algorithms on classification problems.

    Extends the general-purpose individual interface with a getPhenotype() method to get the classifier represented by the individual genotype.

    Author:
    Sebastian Ventura, Amelia Zafra, Jose M. Luna, Alberto Cano, Juan Luis Olmo
